					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">US is 120 volts, 60Hz.  UK is 240 volts, 50Hz; you're going to need a lot more than just an AC adapter, and I have no idea if the polarity on the AC adapters (towards the console) are reversed like they are between the US NES and the Famicom.</div>

